A Monte Carlo simulation approach for estimating the health and economic impact 
of interventions provided at a student-run clinic.

Arenas DJ(1), Lett E(1), Klusaritz H(2), Teitelman AM(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)Perelman School of Medicine, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, PA, 
